                    "name": "Weapon Mount",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "This vehicle has a weapon mount. At purchase, this weapon mount is initially empty. Installing or uninstalling a weapon into the mount requires 3 hours, a successful DC 39 Crafting check, and an appropriate weapon. The mount can be equipped with a Large or smaller ranged siege weapon.",
